graph TD
    START([START]) --> ExtractIntents[Extract Intents<br/>LLM analyzes user prompt<br/>to identify HR intents]
    ExtractIntents --> ValidateWithHuman{Validate with Human<br/>Are intents found?}
    ValidateWithHuman -->|No intents found| ActionCenter[Create Action in<br/>UiPath Action Center<br/>Human validates intents]
    ValidateWithHuman -->|Intents exist| RouteIntents[Route Intents<br/>Print identified intents]
    ActionCenter --> RouteIntents
    RouteIntents --> END([END])
    
    style START fill:#90EE90
    style END fill:#FFB6C1
    style ExtractIntents fill:#87CEEB
    style ValidateWithHuman fill:#FFD700
    style ActionCenter fill:#FFA500
    style RouteIntents fill:#87CEEB
    
    classDef llmNode fill:#87CEEB,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    classDef humanNode fill:#FFA500,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    classDef decisionNode fill:#FFD700,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
